00:15:31,504 --> 00:15:33,504
Tepat seperti yang kau katakan, nak.

295
00:15:33,504 --> 00:15:36,004
Cucuku sedang ikut karyawisata sekolah

296
00:15:36,004 --> 00:15:39,204
